The fashion junkie was invited by creative director of Gucci Alessandro Michele to attend the 2017 and 2018 Women and Men s Fashion Show at the Gucci headquarters. All of Riky s travel arrangements were covered by the renowned brand. The rapper is also scheduled to meet the president of Gucci and chief executive officer Marco Bizzarri and also attend a private presentation. Before jetting off to Italy the lyricist took to twitter to share his excitement. FROM BRAAMFONTEIN TO MILAN chasing your dreams never felt so good #GGLive #GucciFW17 hGrateful. We re really proud of King Kotini and we hope he keeps flying the SA flag up high.